item.title: Zeke Taylor
item.description: Zeke Taylor is an American actor and internet personality. He is best known for his roles in Merman Academy (2015), NicheZeke (2013), Theories with Zeke (2019), Lucid Nonsense (2019), and The Witches (2020).
